### Pack Order (Seller)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders/{{orderId}}/pack
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{sessionCookie}}

### Ship Order (Seller/Admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders/{{orderId}}/ship
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{sessionCookie}}

{
  "awbNumber": "AWB123456789"
}

### Deliver Order (Admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders/{{orderId}}/deliver
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{sessionCookie}}

### Cancel Order (Admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders/{{orderId}}/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{sessionCookie}}

{
  "reason": "Customer requested cancellation"
}

### Create AWB (Seller)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/shipping/awb
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{sessionCookie}}

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "weightKg": 2.5
}

### Download AWB Label
GET http://localhost:3000/api/shipping/awb/{{orderId}}/label
Cookie: {{sessionCookie}}

### Shipping Webhook (Idempotent)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/shipping/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "mock",
  "eventId": "event_123",
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "status": "delivered",
  "meta": {
    "timestamp": "2024-01-15T10:30:00.000Z",
    "location": "Bucharest, Romania"
  }
}

### Get/Create Conversation
GET http://localhost:3000/api/conversations/{{orderId}}
Cookie: {{sessionCookie}}

### Send Message
POST http://localhost:3000/api/messages/{{conversationId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{sessionCookie}}

{
  "body": "Hello, when will my order be shipped?"
}

